sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Reporter
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant CDN as CloudFront (optional)
    participant ALB as ALB + WAF
    participant API as Backend (ECS Task)
    participant SM as Secrets Manager
    participant DB as RDS PostgreSQL
    participant S3 as S3 Bucket
    participant CW as CloudWatch
    participant PR as Prometheus

    U->>FE: Fill incident form and attach file
    FE->>CDN: PUT /api/incidents over HTTPS
    CDN->>ALB: forward
    ALB->>ALB: WAF rules check (SQLi, XSS)
    ALB->>API: POST /api/incidents
    API->>API: JWT middleware verify
    API->>SM: get DB credentials (cached)
    SM-->>API: credentials
    API->>DB: BEGIN tx, INSERT incident, INSERT audit_log
    DB-->>API: incident id
    API->>S3: request presigned PUT URL
    S3-->>API: URL
    API->>DB: INSERT attachment row, COMMIT
    DB-->>API: OK
    API->>CW: structured log CREATE action
    API->>PR: incident_created_total counter increment
    API-->>FE: 201 Created with presigned URL
    FE->>S3: PUT file directly from browser
    S3-->>FE: 200
    FE-->>U: success toast
